sec.p:
While the question is relatively simple, the answer is still up for discussion and the problem itself has led to a long-standing controversy in physics. Early attempts to solve the problem were proposed by Planck1,2 and Einstein3,4. They both proposed the same set of relativistic transformations:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
